<h2>There are $suppliers.size() of $productName</h2>
</br>
List of suppliers :

#set($i=1)
<table class="gridtable">
    <tr>
        <th>Lp.</th>
        <th>Comanpy Name</th>
        <th>City</th>
        <th>Street</th>
        <th>Supplier ID</th>
    </tr>
    #foreach($supplier in $suppliers)
        <tr>
            <td>$i</td>
            <td>$supplier.getCompanyName()</td>
            <td>$supplier.getCity()</td>
            <td>$supplier.getStreet()</td>
            <td>$supplier.getId()</td>
        </tr>
        #set ($i = $i +1)
    #end
</table>
</br>
